# Task #134: fresh pair / nothing played yet — no continue-head.txt. The dispatcher must
# show the honest empty state and touch NOTHING (no engine call, no emulator launch).
desc Continue dispatcher: no head file -> honest empty state, zero side effects
invoke ctpak
config paired
expect_exit 0
expect_trace PRES timeout=4 msg='Nothing to continue yet - play something!'
expect_trace_absent ENGINE
expect_trace_absent EMULAUNCH
